OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAn
OL,6,Fincreasingly cloudy evening and night
OL,7,Fwith some rain mainly affecting
OL,8,Fnorthern parts of the region with some
OL,9,Fheavier bursts likely across the
OL,10,FDerbyshire Hills. Drier later in the
OL,11,Fnight. Gusty winds for most.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FAny early showers or rain
OL,14,Fclearing early Thursday morning, then
OL,15,Fdry and breezy, with some clear or
OL,16,Fsunny spells. Temperatures close to
OL,17,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
